        The hostile plants respond immediately — bioluminescent signals flash, and forces redirect toward the eastern surge.

        Florence commands, "Now, Remedy!"

        Remedy deploys chemicals across the eastern approach — clouds, barriers, aggressive compounds — maximum chaos.

        Florence commands, "Runner, go!"

        Runner dives deep underground, vines cutting through soil toward the command node. I can't see what's happening down there, but I imagine it's intense…
